Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before transitioning to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' across all cases

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before transitioning to 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before any subsequent activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + In Progress' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before transitioning to any subsequent activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases with 'Completed + In Call' activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Average duration between 'Accepted + In Progress' and the next occurrence of 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + In Call' across different organization countries

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases ending with 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Cancelled occurs

Name: Longest and shortest duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases with high impact
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + In Progress' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS filtered by the function ma == 'High' where ma is the last value of impact

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' during the first occurrence in a case versus during subsequent occurrences
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Duration variability of 'Accepted + In Progress' across different products

Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Comparison of average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases with 'Medium' impact versus those with 'High' impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Total cumulative duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' for all cases within the top 10% of longest case durations
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Average lead time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Resolved' in cases involving 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before transitioning to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases with 'Low' impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Median duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' for cases that eventually reach 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Median waiting time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'
